# Everything Loop Local Settings

These settings customize the default behavior of everything-loop for your projects.

## Usage

Place this file at `.claude/everything-loop.local.md` in your project root or `~/.claude/everything-loop.local.md` for global defaults.

## Notes

- Command-line flags override these defaults
- Project-level settings override global settings
- This file should be gitignored (contains local preferences)
